      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior is clean with only minor signs of regular use, and the interior has been kept tidy and smoke-free. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine starts reliably, and it handles well on the road. It has a consistent service history, making it a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, ready-to-drive vehicle.",
